{"tid":202971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急症室加價政府傾向$150至$200","createTime":"2017-04-16T02:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T14:54:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"729635c6f9317e48cb307556299ee63216c7f7b6","tid":202971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"急症室加價　政府傾向$150至$200　<br />\n　<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】醫院管理局去年底建議調整公立醫院多項收費，當中最具爭議性的急症室收費由100元增加至220元。立法會將於下周二（25日）再次討論公立醫院加價事宜，據悉，政府傾向支持急症室加價，藉以減少急症室被濫用的情況；不過，政府傾向的加幅較醫院管理局建議的為低，介乎150元至200元，希望社會較易接受。<br />\n公立醫院2002年開始實施急症室收費，急症室由免費改成收費100元，14年以來沒有調整。醫院管理局去年底建議急症室收費由100元增加至220元，加幅120%；其他服務例如普通科門診則由45元增加至61元，急症病床每日由100元增加至150元等。食物及衞生局早前已經接獲醫院管理局的加費檢討報告，目前正在考慮有關建議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170416&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=19991538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170416%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D19991538&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c8458f93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170416%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D19991538&h=2be7d779\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170416&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=19991538</a>"},{"pid":"bfac339984ff6a38e94516ddcc23ed34a990a828","tid":202971,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"讚成"},{"pid":"d56310ab086311054f6934ccfc2cb2355a7a57c0","tid":202971,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>贊</strong>成"},{"pid":"98ec2e28cd1f306b40f967797c17e4d58bbdf892","tid":202971,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"加到1000就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br